All products contain product specifications, product claims (wherever applicable) including details of the ingredients used in manufacturing the product. The instructions for usage of products are provided on the packaging of the product and are also available/displayed on the Site. You should carefully peruse the specifications/instructions/ingredients provided against each product on the Site. In addition to the same, You should only use the product for Yourself/Your child by adhering to the usage guidelines, storage directions, recommended usage/dosage, ingredient details, and other information related to the product as provided on the Site. If You/ Your child is or may be allergic to any of the ingredients used in a product, You should not use the said product for Yourself/Your child.
Further, if You/Your child is on any medication which may affect the skin/body/hair and/or You are pregnant/lactating, if You/Your child suffers from any skin/hair related disorder, and/or if You/Your child has a skin/body/hair condition which may affect/be likely to affect the skin/body/hair, then kindly consult with Your doctor prior to usage and application of any product. Before every use, test the skin/body/hair reaction by applying the product to a small part of an area preferably on the inside of the wrist, following the directions for use. If after 24 hours there is no adverse reaction, You may continue to use the product. However, if You/Your child experiences any kind of discomfort during use, then remove the product immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation/irritation/discomfort persists, seek immediate medical advice.
