Once You have added all the desired products to Your cart/shopping bag You can proceed to place Your order.
You may review the products in Your cart/shopping bag by clicking on the cart/shopping bag icon on the Site/webpage.
You must follow the onscreen instructions to proceed through the checkout process on the Site. You must always correct any errors in data which You have entered/which is already saved, change/modify the shopping bag contents (basis Your preference), by adding or removing one or more products from the cart/shopping bag before finally placing the order.
At the time of placing the order, the total price along with the breakup price for the different products, details of all the compulsory and voluntary charges, such as delivery charges, postage, and handling charges, etc., and the applicable tax shall be provided to You by displaying the same on the Site.
Once You have confirmed the details of the order, You will be directed to the payment page. BabyChakra provides You with several options for the modes of payment, the details of the modes of payment along with other payment details have been provided under Clause 12 of these Terms of Use and will also be available on the Site.
